{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1784878111938", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "已确认：arXiv 2512.11521（2025年12月12日）为同一作者团队（Peng, Li, Wang）的前序工作，题为“Physics-Informed Cross-Learning for Seismic Acoustic Impedance Inversion and Wavelet Extraction”。当前论文（2607.20989，2026年7月）提出了“RD-SCL”——这显然是一个延续。前序工作已引入了 cross-learning；而本文增加了 regularized deconvolution。"}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "6967764d-7b28-4c88-aaab-fe1705e62b34", "uuid": "a68b327b-224a-4c00-a692-a2caad61cef6"}
